com.tsgrp.migration.event

Class DateOffsetterListener

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.tsgrp.migration.event.AbstractListener
      • com.tsgrp.migration.event.DateOffsetterListener
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    SourceEndExportNodeEventListener, TargetBeginImportNodeEventListener

    public class DateOffsetterListener
extends AbstractListener
implements SourceEndExportNodeEventListener, TargetBeginImportNodeEventListener
    Listener which offsets the value of injected date attributes by an injected value. This offset can be either positive or negative.
